Interface DiscoveryService

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CallContextAwareCmisService, CmisService, ProgressControlCmisService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBindingCmisServiceWrapper, AbstractCmisService, AbstractCmisServiceWrapper, CachedBindingCmisService, CmisServiceWrapper, ConformanceCmisServiceWrapper, FilterCmisService, HttpSessionCmisService, LruCacheCmisService, SimpleForwardingCmisService, SimpleLoggingCmisServiceWrapper

    public interface DiscoveryService
    Discovery Service interface.

    See the CMIS 1.0 and CMIS 1.1 specifications for details on the operations, parameters, exceptions and the domain model.
